problem: Cedar Falls Middle School has students in grades 9996233 – 7 and each year they are challenged to earn as many Accelerated Reader points as they can. The 10 students in each grade with the most points get to try an escape room set up by the teachers. Only 8 students can try the escape room at a time. They have 99962335 minutes to try and escape. If every group uses their full 99962335 minutes, how long will it take for everyone to try the escape room?
